RACE.RACE_TEXT: AJAX DOWNS RACE 1 300 Y Dirt CR: 83. Allowance Purse 11000. For Three Year Olds and Upward Which Have Not Won A Race Since May 1, 2023 and Which Have Started At Ajax Downs Since May 1, 2023.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: CHICKSDIGMYMONEYBAGS prevailed under mild urging. HANOVER HILL THERESA just missed. MOMSEXTRAVAGANTHEART pressed inside, faded. FAST STREAKIN NICK no finishing kick. RAPTER faltered late.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: AJAX DOWNS RACE 2 350 Y Dirt CR: 69. Speed Index Race Purse 9000. For Three Year Olds and Upward With An Average Speed Index Of 80 And Under.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: JOE CHECKERS wire to wire. WILDKATES DYNASTY hopped start, closed well. WAVIN BAC ATYA hard ridden for show. PRITTY COLD evenly to finish. CARAWAYS JET MOON bumped slightly at start.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: MS MEXICAN MOUSE won easily. PAGRANAS BOY game second. BODACIOUS TATAZ closed well outside. KITSAWINNER chased inside, tired late. AZURES ROYALTY no closing kick.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: AJAX DOWNS RACE 4 250 Y Dirt CR: 56. Maiden Purse 10000. For Maidens, Two Years Old.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: SNOW MUCH FUN won going away. IVY LEAGUE SUGARBABY closed very well. SUGAR BOY PERRY game effort inside. YOU ARE THE REASON stumbled at start. NO CASH needed more ground. RUSHIN FOR DOUGH hopped at start.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: A SHADES OF COLD drew away late. FIRSTPRIZE CHARLOTTE second best. ADMIRAL NELSON tired inside. STANAIR mild close. SPEEDY COUNTRY MOUSE no excuse. RUSHN IN THE RAIN rough beginning.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: ADREAMTOBUILDAKISSON never in doubt. EYESA DASHA WACKY second best. DAZ COLD no match, top two. A RUSHN LILLY good effort. TEX DYNASTY no closing kick. RUBY SUNDAY stepped slow at start.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: AJAX DOWNS RACE 7 110 Y Dirt CR: 81. Speed Index Race Purse 10000. For Three Year Olds and Upward With An Average Speed Index Of 90 And Under.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: BODHI never in doubt. JUNOIMZOOMIN good effort. I THINK ICON chased winner. SW SNOWMAGICALLYKOOL gamely in between. MISS ORIENT EXPRESS needed more room. CHEEKO MALO broke outward at start. RUNAWAYLIGHTSNCAVIAR slow start, not a factor.
